{"tid":1310650,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"燃點香煙喝淡酒,上市失敗要敗走","createTime":"2019-07-12T18:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T04:04:12.000Z","uid":57308,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7fb9c51176dc67c0b5edad0c894b5bfc1ca45898","tid":1310650,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T18:59:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新浪美股訊7月13日消息， 百威英博已經暫停其亞太子公司可能融資98億美元的首次公開募股。<br />\n<br />\n這家啤酒巨頭在一份聲明中表示，公司決定停止推進百威亞太公司的IPO。彭博社週五報道稱，百威亞太的香港IPO據悉難以定價。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;由於幾個因素，包括當前市場狀況，公司沒有在推進此項交易，&rdquo;百威英博在聲明中表示。&ldquo;公司將密切關注市場狀況，並基於嚴格的財務紀律持續評估各種選擇，以提高股東價值、優化業務並推動長期增長。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在百威英博決定暫停亞太業務IPO之前，瑞士再保險週四宣佈暫停子公司ReAssure Group Plc規模41億美元的IPO，理由是投資者需求疲軟。<br />\n<br />\n招股説明書顯示，百威亞太公司擬議以每股40至47港元的價格發行16.3億股。<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通和摩根士丹利是聯席保薦人。"},{"pid":"10a431070a02caf74a29f8fa5491f534d88582bb","tid":1310650,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T19:04:27.000Z","msg":"好過夾硬上 跌到仆街嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80be8acc4cdbcb5a2aae1b51ddb96d3852fd929","tid":1310650,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T19:06:06.000Z","msg":"屈淋病啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6173fc9790241caad3bcbe4b64bac92d039ea1df","tid":1310650,"uid":57308,"like":7,"dislike":0,"